Package: robustness
Type: Package
Title: Range Tests for Equality and Equivalence Across Specifications
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-06-28
Authors@R: person("David A.", "Jaeger", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "daj4@st-andrews.ac.uk")
Description: Range-based and Wald-based tests of equality and equivalence
    across a set of specifications, from saved bootstrap draws of the
    coefficient of interest. Implements the method of Jaeger (2026),
    "Robustness? Range Tests for Equality and Equivalence Across
    Specifications." The R counterpart of the Stata 'robustness' command:
    given the same bootstrap draws, the two produce the same statistics.
